The second of my releases on fps
This map runs regularly on the [MAD] server
Let me know if you wish to use it on your server

This map was inspired from math class
We were doing radicals at the time
what else would you like to know?
I used graph paper?

This map is very popular on the MAD server.  its very balanced, and can be played with as few as 2v2 despite it's size.
Please ignore the lagg you get from blowing up 1000 bananas in the market, as its an awesome effect
By the way, both bombsites can ACTUALLY BE DESTROYED
